summary: Cine | Capitana Marvel, en cines el 8 de Marzo.
title: Cine | Capitana Marvel, en cines el 8 de Marzo.
body:
Cine | Capitana Marvel, en cines el 8 de Marzo.

Ambientada en la década de 1990, CAPITANA MARVEL de Marvel Studios nos presenta una original y nueva aventura situada en un período nunca antes visto en el Universo Cinematográfico de Marvel. La historia sigue a Carol Danvers, a quien veremos convertirse en una de las heroínas más poderosas del universo cuando la Tierra queda atrapada en medio de una guerra galáctica entre dos razas alienígenas.

Here’s another Captain Marvel figure. Thank gawd she comes with an alternate head because the Mohawk version looks awful. 
The...
body:
Here’s another Captain Marvel figure. Thank gawd she comes with an alternate head because the Mohawk version looks awful.


The back of the packaging references a figure of the Grey Gargoyle. I scanned his entry on Wikipedia and there one brief reference to Ms. Marvel so he does sound like a regular adversary of hers. No telling whether he’ll be in the movie.

summary: I can’t believe all the hate for Brie and Captain Marvel. Sure I’m concerned about her having a part too big in Endgame and...
body: I can’t believe all the hate for Brie and Captain Marvel. Sure I’m concerned about her having a part too big in Endgame and spoiling our 6 first Avengers, but it doesn’t deserve all the mean comments. Especially if it’s from some unsecure toxic men who feel the need to spit on a female hero just for it. Wait and see, the movie isn’t released yet, and whatever it will be, it’s NOT okay to bully the actress. I really hope Marvel will do right with this film, just to shut them up.
